<bibRefCitation author="BELOKOBYLSKIJ, S. A." box="[324,586,1675,1696]" pageId="5" pageNumber="6" pagination="394 - 416" refId="ref22423" refString="BELOKOBYLSKIJ, S. A. (2002) East Palaearctic species of the braconid wasp genus Synaldis Forster (Hymenoptera, Braconidae, Alysiinae) species without mesoscutal pit. Entomologicheskoye Obozrenie 81 (2): 394 - 416. [In Russian with English title and summary]" type="journal article" year="2002">BELOKOBYLSKIJ 2002: 885</bibRefCitation>
